actionConfiguration.body:
SELECT
	"itemId" AS value,
	CASE
		WHEN "itemId" = 1 THEN 'Yokohama Advan Racnig RCIII'
		WHEN "itemId" = 2 THEN 'Yokohama Advan Racing TCIII'
		WHEN "itemId" = 3 THEN 'Yokohama Super Advan Racing ver.2'
		WHEN "itemId" = 4 THEN 'Yokohama Advan Racing RG-D2'
		WHEN "itemId" = 5 THEN 'Yokohama Advan Racnig RGIII'
		WHEN "itemId" = 6 THEN 'Yokohama Advan Racing RSII'
		WHEN "itemId" = 7 THEN 'Yokohama Advan Racing RS-D'
		WHEN "itemId" = 8 THEN 'Yokohama Model T6'
		WHEN "itemId" = 9 THEN 'Yokohama Advan GT'
		WHEN "itemId" = 11 THEN 'Watanabe Eight Spoke'
		WHEN "itemId" = 12 THEN 'Watanabe Forged Mg Cyclone'
		WHEN "itemId" = 13 THEN 'Watanabe Stellar'
		WHEN "itemId" = 14 THEN 'Watanabe GR-8'
		WHEN "itemId" = 15 THEN 'Watanabe NEW RS-8'
		WHEN "itemId" = 16 THEN 'Rays VR CE28N'
		WHEN "itemId" = 17 THEN 'Rays Gram Lights 57ANA'
		WHEN "itemId" = 18 THEN 'Rays Lucianna Stratagia'
		WHEN "itemId" = 19 THEN 'Rays Gram Lights 57D'
		WHEN "itemId" = 20 THEN 'Rays VR TE37 Saga'
		WHEN "itemId" = 21 THEN 'Rays VR TE037 DURR'
		WHEN "itemId" = 22 THEN 'Rays VR GT-TypeM'
		WHEN "itemId" = 23 THEN 'Rays GA?BANA'
		WHEN "itemId" = 24 THEN 'Rays VR RE30'
		WHEN "itemId" = 27 THEN 'Rays VR ZE40'
		WHEN "itemId" = 28 THEN 'Enkei Performance Line PFM1'
		WHEN "itemId" = 29 THEN 'Enkei Racing RPF1'
		WHEN "itemId" = 30 THEN 'Enkei Racing Revolution NT03RR'
		WHEN "itemId" = 31 THEN 'Enkei WPS JL01'
		WHEN "itemId" = 32 THEN 'Enkei RS05'
		WHEN "itemId" = 33 THEN 'Enkei JS+M'
		WHEN "itemId" = 34 THEN 'Enkei Performance Line PF07'
		WHEN "itemId" = 37 THEN 'OZ Crono-3'
		WHEN "itemId" = 38 THEN 'OZ Rally Racing'
		WHEN "itemId" = 39 THEN 'OZ ForgiataGT'
		WHEN "itemId" = 40 THEN 'OZ Leggenda'
		WHEN "itemId" = 41 THEN 'OZ Superturismo-LM'
		WHEN "itemId" = 42 THEN 'OZ Formula-HLT'
		WHEN "itemId" = 43 THEN 'OZ ZEUS HLT FORGED'
		WHEN "itemId" = 47 THEN 'BBS RI-D'
		WHEN "itemId" = 48 THEN 'BBS RI-A'
		WHEN "itemId" = 49 THEN 'BBS FS'
		WHEN "itemId" = 50 THEN 'BBS RG-R'
		WHEN "itemId" = 51 THEN 'BBS Super-RS'
		WHEN "itemId" = 53 THEN 'BBS LM'
		WHEN "itemId" = 54 THEN 'BBS FZ-MG'
		ELSE '未知轮毂，请向管理员报告此错误'
	END AS label
FROM public."CarItem"
WHERE "carId" = {{SelectCarId.selectedOptionValue}} AND "category" = 2
UNION

SELECT
    0 AS value,
    '原厂轮毂' AS label
ORDER BY value ASC;
SELECT pg_sleep(3);
